               <provenance>In Additiones 1 and 2, ʾabuna Gabra Ḥǝywat is mentioned as the donor. 
                     ʾAbuna Gabra Māryām is mentioned in the
                     supplication formulas, possibly the same person as in Mss. MAKM-002, MAKM-007.
                        ʾAbuna Gabra ʾƎgziabǝḥer and ʾabuna Zarʾa Buruk are mentioned in the supplication
                     formula on 54rb, and Walatta Madḫǝn on 59vb.</provenance></history>
